extends layout

block content
  img(src="images/sinaichrist.jpg", alt="Sinai Christ", align="right", width=400)
  h1 Welcome to the Kingdom of Cyprus
  p Welcome to the website of the #[strong Kingdom of Cyprus], an ark designed to preserve all that is good in both the Christian faith and the English nation in these troubled times.

  if loggedIn
    h2 Interesting Pages
    p There are so many ways you could begin your journey...
    ul
      li #[a(href="territories/kingdom") A description of the Kingdom];
      li #[a(href="canons") Hosker's Canons</a>];
      li #[a(href="search") Search] this site.
  else
    h2 Log In
    p Please log in to continue.
    form(action="/login", method="post")
      p
        | Username: 
        input(type="text", name="username")
      p
        | Password: 
        input(type="password", name="password")
      input(type="submit", value="Submit")
